@cite{@value{PACKAGE_TITLE}} is a general purpose tool for measuring bandwidth and performance of
the @cite{Internet Protocol} suite.  The @cite{OpenSS7 Modified @value{PACKAGE_TITLE}} package is an
@uref{http://www.openss7.org, OpenSS7 Project} release of the DAST @code{iperf} package configured
to run with @cite{OpenSS7 Linux Native Stream Control Transmission Protocol (SCTP)}.

This is a version of the @dfn{Iperf} package released by the @cite{University of Illinois} modified
by the @uref{http://www.openss7.org/, OpenSS7 Project} for use with @cite{OpenSS7 SCTP (Stream
Control Transmission Protocol)}.  This @cite{OpenSS7} release of the package is based on the
@dfn{Iperf-2.0.0} release from the @cite{University of Illinois}.

